data.description: Come see this charming home in Rosemont.  This spacious home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and one half bathroom, with a 2 car garage.  It also has a bonus room and another room that can be used as an office.   If you are looking for space, this home offers just that! In addition, when the temperatures outside are too frigid for your taste, you can cozy up in front of the fireplace that this home boasts. It has a screened patio and spacious fenced/walled back yard.  THIS IS A MUST SEE!
